 is a logistical challenge unlike any I've handled before. I know some of you are staying up very late. Be patient, please <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  . We'll get it rolling as fast and as smoothly as possible. Once break-in is accomplished (IMHO the hard part) the fun will begin. Groups will be posted by 5pm PST(8pm EST). Take a look to see where you are, please. Remember, the groups may change, but will be adhered to as closely as possible.<br><br>Now, for a few rules. <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Follow instructions</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->. You will be told when and with whom to group with. Do it as fast as possible. <br><br>During break-in there will be times to camp out. If you're told to camp, do it (<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> not /quit</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> it must be /camp). No questions. Sit and camp. We'll have a chat room to go to for reentrance. On entering the chat room announce who you are. Instructions will follow.<br><br>Important on break-in. Follow your guide. If you get aggro. DIE DIE DIE. Don't run. Just stand and die. You will be rezzed. Better one death than the whole raid.<br><br>Here is a link to a printable map. The red line is the route you will be taking to camp. <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.deadzed.com/eq/images/poh.jpg">Printable map</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->. Ok, once at camp <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> DON'T</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> Wander We have a pull team setup so Stay Put.<br><br>ASSIST when told to, NOT BEFORE. This can't be stressed enough. Assist when the command is given. A melee assist and a separate caster assist will be called. Pay attention to it.<br><br>NO AoE's. Not even sure this needs to be said, but an AoE could easily cause a wipe. Don't use them. Pretend you don't have them.<br><br>If things get nasty. PROTECT THE CLERICS. Clerics will camp. Everyone else do what you can to keep aggro off of them. When clerics are camped, everyone else can camp. Again <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Don't /q</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->. Camp. An LD character can have melee aggro and be dragged somewhere. So camp. But once again, PROTECT THE CLERICS.<br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Loot</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>We are claiming the Book of Souls and The Corrupter of Life's skull as hosts. All other drops will be rolled on. Rolling will be 10*level. When a no drop item drops, stats will be called with eligible classes. Roll and if you win, loot. Winner will be announced. One item each please until all eligible contenders have gotten an item.<br><br>Notable drops for epics:<br>Corrupter of Life---skull for Airiaz's Nature's Defender (claimed)<br>Maestro of Rancor---hand is for warrior epic<br>Thought Corrupter---Tainted Dark steel BP for SK epic<br>Forsaken Revenant---essence of vampire for chanter epic<br>Ashenbone Drake---decrepit hide for SK epic<br>Underboss random---shattered emerald of corruption for Rng epic<br>Book of Souls---Spawned for Ombres' epic (claimed)<br><br>The rest of the loot table is <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/itemzone.html?zone=68">here</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->. I was going to make a list of class-specific drops, but frankly I haven't had time. Make a list of stuff you want if you like. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br><br>Finally. Have fun. If you're not having fun, we'll get you out so you can do something else. I can't imagine why you wouldn't be having fun, though <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p>Faedaer Ryverwalker<BR>Siege Captain<BR>Keeper of the Fist <BR>Woodland Priest of Tunare<BR></p><span class=m><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub95.